# 📊 Ecosystem Tokenomics & Strategic Roadmap

This document outlines the multi-stage economic framework of the *CopyCat Ecosystem*. Designed by a 35-year TradFi veteran, these mechanics prioritize liquidity depth, deflationary pressure, and long-term holder incentives.

---

## 🛠️ Phase 1: The Bonding Curve (Bootstrap Stage)
Initial tokens are launched via *Jupiter Studio* using a *Dynamic Bonding Curve (DBC)*. This stage is dedicated to accumulating the "War Chest" (Treasury) required for independent, professional launches.

### Transaction Parameters
* *Bundled Launch:* Token creation and initial liquidity seeding occur in a single atomic transaction to neutralize front-running snipers.
* *Buy Tax:* 0.1% (Minimal friction for entry).
* *Sell Tax:* 5.9% (Captures volatility and penalizes short-term exit).

### Revenue Allocation (Stage 1)
| Allocation | Percentage | Purpose |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| *Liquidity Treasury* | 80% | Funding independent liquidity for Stage 2 launches. |
| *Marketing* | 10% | Direct promotion for the specific trending token. |
| *Buy-Back & Burn* | 10% | Immediate deflationary pressure on the token supply. |

---

## 🚀 Phase 2: Independent Liquidity (Maturity Stage)
Once the Treasury reaches sustainable levels, we transition to direct DEX listings on *Jupiter/Raydium* without a bonding curve.

### Launch Logic
* *Fixed Supply:* 100,000,000,000 (100B) tokens per launch.
* *Standardized Price:* Every new token starts at a consistent entry valuation.
* *Cadence:* Maximum of *2 launches per week* to ensure focus and prevent market exhaustion.

### Revenue Allocation (Stage 2)
| Allocation | Percentage | Purpose |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| *Buy-Back & Burn* | 25% | Aggressive deflationary mechanism. |
| *Marketing* | 25% | Funding social rewards, mods, and high-tier promotions. |
| *$COPYCAT Fund* | 25% | Dedicated capital to buy-back and burn the principal ecosystem token. |
| *Admin/Dev* | 25% | Operational expenses and ecosystem maintenance. |

---

## 🔐 Staking & The Airdrop Loop
We reward the "Diamond Hands" of the ecosystem through a 20-week loyalty cycle.

### The Mechanism
1. *Stake:* Holders of earlier tokens stake their balance in the "Genie Portal."
2. *Snapshot:* A snapshot is taken prior to every new Stage 2 launch.
3. *Distribute:* 10% of the new token's supply is set aside for stakers.
4. *Pro-Rata:* You receive tokens based on your quantity of staked tokens, regardless of market value.

### Vesting Schedule (The 5/20 Rule)
* *Duration:* 20 Weeks.
* *Release:* 5% of tokens are unlocked every 7 days.
* *Objective:* Prevents "dump-on-listing" behavior and encourages long-term ecosystem participation.

---

## 💎 $COPYCAT: The Principal Asset
$COPYCAT is the core utility and value-accrual token of the entire ecosystem.

* *Format:* Standard SPL Token (No Taxes).
* *Listing:* Targeted for Centralized Exchanges (CEX).
* *Deflation:* 25% of all Stage 2 fees from every peripheral token are used to buy back and permanently burn $COPYCAT from the open market.

